  "original_title": "\u0b95\u0bcb\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbe\u0baa\u0baf\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bc6\u0bb3\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bc7\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bae\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Arrival and exodus of Gotabaya",
      "author": "Vishnu",
      "body_lines": [
        "Gotabaya Rajapaksa, the 7th executive president of Sri Lanka, who has a military background without direct participation in politics, has resigned due to the pressure of the people's spontaneous protests. Speaker Mahindayapa Abeywardena has announced that he has received his official letter of resignation.",
        "In the presidential election held on 16 November 2019, Gotabaya Rajapaksa won a massive victory with 69 lakh 24 thousand 255 votes. He got 52.25 percent of the preference votes. Gotabaya Rajapaksa received more votes in the 8th presidential election in 2019 than the candidates who won in the 7 presidential elections from 1982 to 2015 in the history of Sri Lanka.",
        "He held important positions in the army and was also seen as the first president of Sri Lanka with a military background. He retired from the army at an early stage and went to the United States and served as the defense secretary in 2005 when his brother Mahinda Rajapaksa was elected president. After the 2015 regime change, he had a bit of a break from active politics, but he won the 2019 presidential election by a landslide.",
        "National security and economic development were seen as the main issues in his election policy declaration.",
        "However, due to improper economic approaches and irresponsible decisions, Sri Lanka's downfall is due to his rule. He has received the support of more than 69 lakh people, but he has been forced to resign due to the hatred of the people of the entire country.",
        "Because of this, Gotabaya Rajapaksa is the first executive president to resign before the end of his term in Sri Lankan political history. Due to the decisions taken by him, all the people, starting from the farmers, have faced severe hardships without any discrimination. The people enraged by the crisis and the peaceful uprisings of the young generation hoping for a change in the Sri Lankan political system took Gotabaya Rajapaksa to the point of announcing his resignation from another country.",
        "His resignation has taught a great lesson to all politicians that a country should not be managed and how responsible the next rulers should be. Although this resignation will not immediately solve the problems in the country, it is the position of most that Gotabaya Rajapaksa has escaped from being held responsible for all these."
      ],
